==English==
===Noun===
'''sigma'''
# The name for the eighteenth letter of the [[Classical Greek|Classical]] and [[Modern Greek]], the nineteenth letter of [[Old Greek|Old]] and [[Ancient Greek|Ancient]].
# ''(mathematics):'' the symbol ('''Σ''') is used to indicate summation of a set or series.
# ''(statistics):'' the symbol ('''σ''') is used to indicate one [[standard deviation]] from the [[mean]], particularly in a [[normal distribution]].

